abstract: Goldman Sachs and its chief executive Lloyd C. Blankfein is behind a deal to help bankroll a new $100 million stadium catering and merchandising venture for the New York Yankees and the Dallas Cowboys, The New York Post reported.
lead_paragraph: Goldman Sachs and its chief executive Lloyd C. Blankfein is behind a deal to help bankroll a new $100 million stadium catering and merchandising venture for the New York Yankees and the Dallas Cowboys, The New York Post reported.

headline.main: Goldman Behind New Stadium-Concession Venture, Report Says
